<plot>In the fifth of a series of cartoons featuring Quark, the ugly troll from _Valhalla (1986)_ (qv), Quark flies to the North Pole, where he finds Santa Claus struggling to deliver Christmas presents in time. Quark's actions alternate between helping and troubling Santa and bring them both through the snow landscapes and to the house of Quark's parents.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?366589</url></doc>
